    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great and hits the road smoothly, this is the one. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home where it'll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
