    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six independent throttle bodies. Mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with consistent engagement. The chassis has been inspected for rear subframe fatigue, and the VANOS system has been serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Riding on a factory-tuned suspension with refreshed bushings, it offers the precise turn-in and communicative feedback expected of the marque. While the finish shows minor road-wear consistent with its history, the mechanical integrity remains the priority, making this a driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
