    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my ride. This car has been such a reliable companion for me, and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved over the years. The interior is nice and tidy, and it still drives like a total dream. It\u2019s the perfect fit for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great out on the road. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I\u2019d love to help you get behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
