    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, a quintessential driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example features a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the Double VANOS system has been overhauled to maintain peak torque across the rev range. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and heavy-duty dampers, preserving the chassis's legendary communicative handling. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, making it an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking performance over a garage queen.",
